/* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   Particle Neural Network  —  7 layers, 45 nodes
   Nodes: glowing spheres (no orbit clusters)
   Edges: CPU-lerp stream particles
   Transparent canvas — floats over page background
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

